data.description: Exciting opportunity to shape your dream home and complete upgrades that you would like to see! Please see further details below:   Welcome to 3065 Milky Way Dr, a beautifully appointed 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom townhome nestled at the edge of a peaceful York neighborhood. Spanning 1,538 square feet, this end-of-row gem combines comfort with modern living.  Interior Highlights:  Spacious Family Room: Unwind in the expansive family room, featuring a cozy fireplace and two symmetrical windows that frame the picturesque backyard view. Modern Convenience: Enjoy the ease of new appliances included with your purchase, enhancing your culinary experiences in a kitchen designed for functionality and style. Comfortable Living Spaces: With three generously sized bedrooms, this home promises a personal retreat for everyone in the family. Exterior Features:  Private Backyard Oasis: Step outside to a fenced-in backyard, perfect for relaxation or entertaining. The deck offers a tranquil space for outdoor dining or simply enjoying the breeze, while a useful shed provides extra storage. Attached Garage: Benefit from the convenience and security of an attached garage, keeping your vehicle and tools safe and accessible. Location Perks:  Family-Friendly Neighborhood: Situated in a quiet, welcoming community, this home is ideally positioned with immediate access to a local elementary school and library. Proximity to Hanover: Just on the outskirts of Hanover, enjoy the charm and amenities this town offers. Explore the rich history and vibrant culture in downtown Hanover.   The owner has partnered with a local company to allow you to customize the kitchen, bathrooms, and needed upgrades. To take advantage of this opportunity submit an offer and turn this house into your dream home – a perfect collaboration between your vision and the potential this property holds.
